<section style="padding:60px 0">
  <div class="engine" id="engine">
    <div class="engine-inner">
      <span class="tag">The "Auto-Pilot" Lead Engine</span>
      <h2>Turn Your Website Into A 24/7 Sales Rep That Never Takes A Sickie.</h2>
      <p class="sub">The Last Thing You Want Is To Be Glued To Your Phone Chasing A Lead Who Filled Out A Form Three Days Ago — By Then They've Called Your Mate Down The Road. We Sort That Out, So It Runs While You Have Your Flat White.</p>
      <div class="progress"><span id="prog"></span></div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step on" data-step="0">
          <div class="ick"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9z"/></svg></div>
          <span class="n">Step 01</span>
          <h3>Instant Response</h3>
          <p>Your New Lead Gets A Text And Email Within 60 Seconds. No More "Sorry I Missed Your Call."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" data-step="1">
          <div class="ick"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-9-9c2.5 0 4.78 1 6.4 2.6"/><path d="M21 4v5h-5"/></svg></div>
          <span class="n">Step 02</span>
          <h3>Smart Follow-Up</h3>
          <p>If They Don't Reply, The System Gently Nudges Them For A Week With Useful Info Until They're Ready To Book.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" data-step="2">
          <div class="ick"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18M9 16l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
          <span class="n">Step 03</span>
          <h3>Bookings Sorted</h3>
          <p>They Pick A Time That Suits Them, Straight Into Your Calendar. No Back-And-Forth Emails.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
